                </svg></span><span class="absolute w-[1px] h-[1px] overflow-hidden">The CRFT</span> Lookup, a free Pagespeed Insights alternative</h1>
                <p class="text-center text-pretty lg:text-xl text-lg mt-5 text-neutral-300 mb-7">The CRFT Lookup is the free alternative to Pagespeed Insights for Lighthouse benchmarks, with added technology detection, meta tag previews and sitemap visualization for a complete view of a website's technical profile.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-row gap-3 mb-10">
                    <a href="/lookup" class="primary-cta">Scan a website</a>
                    <!-- <a href="/audit" class="secondary-cta">See example report</a> -->
                </div>
                <Image src={LookupOverview} alt="Screenshot of CRFT Lookup report on TailwindCSS" class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl"/>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="mt-20">
            <LookupMarquee/>
        </section>
        <section>
            <LookupFeatures/>
        </section>
