        <section>
            <LookupCTA/>
        </section>
        <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-center leading-tight mb-10 text-neutral-300">Your questions, answered</h2>
                <FAQItem
                    question="What makes CRFT Lookup different from Pagespeed Insights?"
                    answer="While both tools analyze website performance, CRFT Lookup goes beyond by detecting technologies used to build the site, showing detailed meta tag previews, and providing comprehensive Lighthouse scoring - all in one place. Pagespeed Insights focuses mainly on performance metrics, while we give you the complete technical picture."
                />
                <FAQItem
                    question="Which tool provides more detailed performance data?"
                    answer="Both CRFT Lookup and Pagespeed Insights use Lighthouse for performance analysis. However, CRFT Lookup contextualizes these metrics alongside the detected technologies, helping you understand how your tech stack impacts performance. We also retain historical data to track improvements over time."
                />
                <FAQItem
                    question="Can I get the same technology detection with Pagespeed Insights?"
                    answer="No, Pagespeed Insights doesn't include technology detection. CRFT Lookup analyzes your site's code, headers, and scripts to identify over 2,500 different technologies - from frameworks and CMS platforms to analytics tools and infrastructure. This helps you understand exactly how sites are built."
                />
                <FAQItem
                    question="Which tool is better for SEO analysis?"
                    answer="While Pagespeed Insights includes basic SEO metrics, CRFT Lookup provides additional context through our meta tag preview feature. You can see exactly how your site appears across search engines, social media, and messaging platforms - helping you optimize your site's presence everywhere it matters."
                />
                <FAQItem
                    question="Do I need to use both tools?"
                    answer="CRFT Lookup includes all the core functionality of Pagespeed Insights plus additional features like technology detection and meta tag previews. While you can use both, CRFT Lookup provides a more comprehensive analysis in a single tool. And like Pagespeed Insights, it's completely free to use."
                />
            </div>
